data.oai_dc:dc: Ecology of the Lahontan Cutthroat Trout in Independence Lake, California

MASTERS THESIS: The present study considers the various aspects of age and growth, food habits, reproduction, and trout-beaver relationship for the Lahontan cutthroat in Independence Lake. It is hoped that the findings of this study will aid in maintaining and managing the cutthroat trout in independence Lake and other waters where this species exists in its native state.
